        <abstract> 
<p>Offers different explanations [from CD’s in <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>] for movements of dogs after voiding, and for their turning around before lying down.</p> 
            <p>CD is also wrong in saying hares do not cry except when they suffer.</p>
